<H2 ALIGN="CENTER"><A NAME="top">This is the homepage for the Software Architect's Wellness Program!</A>

</H2>
<H3><A NAME="item1">Goal:</A></H3>

      
       The goal of the program is to help motivate you to exercise and keep holiday weight off! 


<H3><A NAME="item2">The Program:</A></H3>

	  
The program will run for the months of October, November, and December.  To successfully 
complete the program, you need to exercise on at least half of the days in these months.
The following are examples of exercises: walking, swimming, running, and weight lifting. 
There are certain activities that count for two days worth of exercise.  For a list, 
<A HREF="sarkActivityList.asp">click here!</A> At the end of the program, 
those who are successful  in reaching the goal will receive a Software Architect's 
shirt! 

<H3><A NAME="item3">Requirements:</A></H3>

      In order to participate in the program, a 10 dollar fee is required.  If you are unsuccessful
      at the program, you will receive the 10 dollars back at the Christmas party.




